name: Diamond - Dinosaur
description:
Dino - 10th of 10 art from the "Diamond Animals" collection.
Recently, paleontologists have discovered well-preserved dinosaur DNA from which, if desired, you can clone a real individual. Until then, take a look at this hilarious running diamond tyrannosaurus.
This is the latest art from the "Diamond Animals" collection
